  rerun 2/3 exit: 0   (node_modules present => skipped npm ci, straight to lint) Tests 234 passed | 1 skipped
  rerun 3/3 exit: 0                                                              Tests 234 passed | 1 skipped
  shuffle   exit: 0   (npm run verify -- --sequence.shuffle)                     Tests 234 passed | 1 skipped
  grep -c "eslint: command not found" across all 4 logs: 0

